metadata.name: Lyrical Lemonade Carton #1
metadata.description: 'The Carton' is a collection of 500 unique, handcrafted versions of the Lyrical Lemonade logo. Each carton was created by our in-house design team and offers a refreshing take on the classic logo. Carton ownership grants exclusive access to the world of Lyrical Lemonade. More details available @ www.l3monworldwide.com
